Cell[TextData[StyleBox["Source: USITC estimates. Total import data were \
obtained from the USITC\[CloseCurlyQuote]s DataWeb.The use of aluminum by \
downstream industry was calculated using the Bureau of Economic Analysis \
(BEA) 2012 Use Table and 2012 Import Matrix with adjustments by industry \
analysts as necessary. For more information on the steps taken to calculate \
these values, see Appendix F of the report.\nUSITC, \
\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]DataWeb/Census,\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] accessed \
September 28, 2022. BEA, \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]Input-Output Accounts Data,\
\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] accessed October 17, 2022. ",
 FontSlant->"Italic"]], "Text",
